<h4>Department Description</h4>
<p>The Department of Music at Brigham Young University&ndash;Idaho is an accredited institutional member of the National Association of Schools of Music.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The Department is housed in the Eliza R. Snow Center for the Performing Arts, a beautiful and well-equipped facility. The faculty and facilities provide a superior environment for the serious student of music. In addition, the Department offers a diversity of opportunities for the non-music major to develop musical skills.</p>
<h4></h4>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>BYU&ndash;Idaho Department of Music has an open enrollment policy for all freshmen and transfer students desiring to pursue a degree in music. All are initially considered &ldquo;Prospective Music Majors.&rdquo; Admission as a &ldquo;Music Major&rdquo; and clearance for subsequent courses is contingent upon a Department review of the student&rsquo;s abilities and grades.</p>
<h4></h4>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4>The Department of Music offers four types of degrees:</h4>
<p>--Bachelor of Arts</p>
<p>--Bachelor of Musical Arts</p>
<p>--Bachelor of Music in Education</p>
<p>--Bachelor of Music in Performance. The Bachelor of Arts in Music degree (B.A.) is a liberal arts degree designed to give students a broad education with an emphasis in music.</p>]]></IntroCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="CellGroup" label="Cells" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true"><numColumns type="enumeration" values="1 2 3 4 5" label="Select number of cell columns." readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">4</numColumns><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Cell" Name="CellList" label="Cell List" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="true"><xPower Type="Component" Component="x27310" Name="Cell" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x27311" Name="Cell" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x27312" Name="Cell" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x27313" Name="Cell" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="false"/></xPower></xPower><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_BannerAd" Name="BannerAds" label="Rotating Ads (650x216px required)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="BannerAd" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="" Query="" Name="DeptEvents" label="Define Your Events Folder" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="fals